Version 2.11:
- [+] 03 Aug 2007, Alien - Improvement (0023724): The 2Checkout environment was changed, an ability to work correctly in the new environment was implemented.

Version 2.10:
- [+] 08 Jan 2007, Sheriff - Improvement (0011464): 2Checkout response verification procedure was improved.

Version 2.9:
- [!] 19 Oct 2006, Sheriff - Bug (0012164): A customer is now always redirected back to shopping cart after the payment process at 2Checkout has been completed.. Fixed.

Version 2.8:
- [!] 21 Apr 2005, Sheriff - Bug: Sometimes when HTTPS was turned on, "Approved URL" link would be displayed in the wrong way in module' configuration dialogue. Fixed.

Version 2.7:
- [!] 05 Apr 2005, Sheriff - Bug: Unacceptable symbols were entered into the product name/description field in the process of checkout. Fixed.

Version 2.6:
- [+] 28 Mar 2005, Sheriff - Improvement: The ability to support new additional parameters required in the new version of 2Checkout.com payment gateway is added (the information about ordered products and gift certificates is added to the request to the payment gateway).
- [!] 07 Mar 2005, Asd - Bug: The compiled code/templates cache was not cleaned up during the module uninstallation. Fixed.

Version 2.5:
- [!] 01 Mar 2005, Sheriff - Bug: The misspelling in the function name sometimes caused malfunction in checkout process (the browser has got the http 500 error). Fixed.

Version 2.4:
- [+] 04 Feb 2005, Sheriff - Improvement: The ability to use the new version (2CO Version 2) of the payment gateway interface was added.

Version 2.3:
 - [!] 22 Dec 2004, Sheriff - Bug: Under certain conditions the behavior of some functions was changed on PHP 4.3.10 with some Zend enhancements ('unset()' function, for example). Fixed (additional verification was added). 


